The test will fails on non mac since the test tries load UIManager.setLookAndFeel(&quot;com.apple.laf.AquaLookAndFeel&quot;); which is for mac os look and feel. This test is added a part of <a href="https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8054572">https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8054572</a> <br/>
This is a test bug adding the following will solve the problem where we specify the test to run only on mac os.<br/>
@requires (os.family == &quot;mac&quot;)
